  "detailed_description": "VR Model Viewer allows you to import a variety of model formats for viewing in VR. Supported formats:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- OBJ, 3DS, FBX, STL, DXF, DAE, X3D, Blend, GLTF, PLY, 3MF<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOnce imported you can rotate/scale the model, pick it up and examine it close up in VR, and create custom layouts for displaying your models for later use. Curate your 3D model collection and show off your work!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe following headsets are officially supported:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Valve Index<br />\r\n- HTC Vive<br />\r\n- Oculus Rift CV1<br />\r\n- WMR (Lenovo Explorer)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQuest and Cosmos are not supported at this time.",
  "about_the_game": "VR Model Viewer allows you to import a variety of model formats for viewing in VR. Supported formats:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- OBJ, 3DS, FBX, STL, DXF, DAE, X3D, Blend, GLTF, PLY, 3MF<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOnce imported you can rotate/scale the model, pick it up and examine it close up in VR, and create custom layouts for displaying your models for later use. Curate your 3D model collection and show off your work!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe following headsets are officially supported:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Valve Index<br />\r\n- HTC Vive<br />\r\n- Oculus Rift CV1<br />\r\n- WMR (Lenovo Explorer)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQuest and Cosmos are not supported at this time.",
